Token.Abstract: The RFC 5646 language code for the input text. If you don't specify a language code, Amazon Comprehend detects the dominant language. If you specify the code for a language that Amazon Comprehend does not support, it returns and UnsupportedLanguageException. For more information about RFC 5646, see Tags for Identifying Languages on the IETF Tools web site.
